10.
2674Atītārammaṇaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca atītārammaṇo dhammo uppajjati napurejātapaccayā—  arūpe atītārammaṇaṃ ekaṃ khandhaṃ paṭicca…pe…  dve khandhe…pe…  paṭisandhikkhaṇe…pe… . (1)
2675Anāgatārammaṇaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca anāgatārammaṇo dhammo uppajjati napurejātapaccayā—  arūpe anāgatārammaṇaṃ ekaṃ khandhaṃ paṭicca tayo khandhā…pe…  dve khandhe…pe… . (1)
2676Paccuppannārammaṇaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca paccuppannārammaṇo dhammo uppajjati napurejātapaccayā—  paṭisandhikkhaṇe paccuppannārammaṇaṃ ekaṃ khandhaṃ paṭicca…pe…  dve khandhe…pe… . (1)
